==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Cheep
<hw>Cheep</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To give expression to in a
chirping tone.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Cheep</qex> and twitter twenty million loves.</q>
<rj><qau>Tennyson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cheep</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Cheep
<hw>Cheep</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A chirp, peep, or squeak, as of a
young bird or mouse.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cheer</ent>⟦br⟧
